Shri Mataji: Too many mantras already.

08:14.480 --> 08:15.200
Just see My Feet.

08:16.080 --> 08:20.480
Just see My Feet, how much swollen they\h
are, it’s with the mantras and things.

08:20.480 --> 08:25.760
So it’s better that, this puja business\h
is too much, you see, continuously,\h\h

08:25.760 --> 08:29.680
I’m having, I had how many pujas\h
you know, this short time five.

