08:48.400 --> 08:52.160
But it’s nice that there was puja so\h
everybody could travel, come down, and,\h\h

08:52.720 --> 09:00.880
I agreed to it but you know only fifteen days\h
[HINDI], in twenty days [HINDI] less than that.

